---
const layers = [
  {
    num: 4,
    name: "Protocol",
    color: "#D76D77",
    items: [
      { text: "MCP Server/Client", href: "/features/protocols/" },
      { text: "A2A Server/Client", href: "/features/protocols/" },
      { text: "REST/SSE" },
      { text: "gRPC" },
      { text: "WebSocket" },
      { text: "Framework Adapters" },
    ],
  },
  {
    num: 3,
    name: "Infrastructure",
    color: "#ffca7b",
    items: [
      { text: "Guard Pipeline", href: "/features/guardrails/" },
      { text: "Circuit Breaker" },
      { text: "Retry" },
      { text: "Caching" },
      { text: "Auth (RBAC/ABAC)" },
      { text: "HITL" },
      { text: "Durable Workflows" },
    ],
  },
  {
    num: 2,
    name: "Capability",
    color: "#5CA3CA",
    items: [
      { text: "LLM", href: "/features/llm/" },
      { text: "Agents", href: "/features/agents/" },
      { text: "Tools" },
      { text: "Memory" },
      { text: "RAG", href: "/features/rag/" },
      { text: "Voice", href: "/features/voice/" },
    ],
  },
  {
    num: 1,
    name: "Foundation",
    color: "#3a1c71",
    items: [
      { text: "Schema" },
      { text: "Stream (iter.Seq2)" },
      { text: "Config" },
      { text: "Observability (OTel GenAI)" },
      { text: "Transport" },
    ],
  },
];
---

<section class="arch-section">
  <div class="arch-inner">
    <div class="arch-header">
      <h2 class="arch-heading">
        Layered architecture. <span class="arch-heading-muted">Clean separation of concerns.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="arch-subtitle">Dependencies flow downward. Every layer is independently extensible.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Layer bars -->
    <div class="arch-layers">
      {layers.map((layer) => (
        <div class="arch-layer" style={`--layer-color: ${layer.color}`}>
          <div class="arch-layer-label">
            <span class="arch-layer-num">L{layer.num}</span>
            <span class="arch-layer-name">{layer.name}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="arch-layer-items">
            {layer.items.map((item) =>
              item.href ? (
                <a href={item.href} class="arch-layer-item arch-layer-link">{item.text}</a>
              ) : (
                <span class="arch-layer-item">{item.text}</span>
              )
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}

      <!-- Flow arrow indicator -->
      <div class="arch-flow" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="16" height="40" viewBox="0 0 16 40" fill="none">
          <path d="M8 0v32M2 26l6 8 6-8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
        </svg>
        <span class="arch-flow-label">Dependencies flow down</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Expandable detail cards -->
    <div class="arch-details">
      <details class="arch-detail">
        <summary class="arch-detail-summary">
          <span class="arch-detail-tag" style="--layer-color: #3a1c71">Foundation</span>
          <span class="arch-detail-title">Core primitives and shared types</span>
          <svg class="arch-detail-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="arch-detail-body">
          <p>Core primitives, shared schema types, configuration loading with hot-reload, and OpenTelemetry observability using GenAI semantic conventions. Zero external dependencies beyond stdlib and OTel.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="arch-detail">
        <summary class="arch-detail-summary">
          <span class="arch-detail-tag" style="--layer-color: #5CA3CA">Capability</span>
          <span class="arch-detail-title">LLM, Agents, RAG, Voice, and more</span>
          <svg class="arch-detail-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="arch-detail-body">
          <p>LLM abstraction with router and structured output, agent runtime with planners and handoffs, tool system, MemGPT 3-tier memory, RAG pipeline with hybrid retrieval, and frame-based voice processing.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="arch-detail">
        <summary class="arch-detail-summary">
          <span class="arch-detail-tag" style="--layer-color: #ffca7b">Infrastructure</span>
          <span class="arch-detail-title">Safety, resilience, and operations</span>
          <svg class="arch-detail-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="arch-detail-body">
          <p>Three-stage guard pipeline for input/output/tool safety, circuit breaker and retry resilience, exact and semantic caching, RBAC/ABAC auth, human-in-the-loop approval, and durable workflow execution.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="arch-detail">
        <summary class="arch-detail-summary">
          <span class="arch-detail-tag" style="--layer-color: #D76D77">Protocol</span>
          <span class="arch-detail-title">Interoperability and transport</span>
          <svg class="arch-detail-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="arch-detail-body">
          <p>MCP server and client for tool interoperability, A2A for agent-to-agent communication, REST/SSE endpoints, gRPC services, and HTTP framework adapters for Gin, Fiber, Echo, and Chi.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .arch-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .arch-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .arch-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .arch-heading {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    color: var(--color-light, #f6f6f6);
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-heading {
    color: var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818);
  }

  .arch-heading-muted {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-light, #f6f6f6) 40%, transparent);
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-heading-muted {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818) 40%, transparent);
  }

  .arch-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-light, #f6f6f6) 55%, transparent);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-subtitle {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818) 55%, transparent);
  }

  /* Layer bars */
  .arch-layers {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .arch-layer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-dark, #151515) 80%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-light, #f6f6f6) 6%, transparent);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--layer-color);
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-layer {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-dark, #f7f7f7) 80%, transparent);
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818) 6%, transparent);
    border-left-color: var(--layer-color);
  }

  .arch-layer:hover {
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--layer-color) 40%, transparent);
    border-left-color: var(--layer-color);
  }

  .arch-layer-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.875rem 1rem;
    min-width: 140px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-right: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-light, #f6f6f6) 6%, transparent);
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-layer-label {
    border-right-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818) 6%, transparent);
  }

  .arch-layer-num {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--layer-color) 20%, transparent);
    color: var(--layer-color);
    font-family: "SF Mono", "Fira Code", monospace;
  }

  .arch-layer-name {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-light, #f6f6f6);
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-layer-name {
    color: var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818);
  }

  .arch-layer-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.875rem 1rem;
  }

  .arch-layer-item {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-light, #f6f6f6) 55%, transparent);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-light, #f6f6f6) 4%, transparent);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-layer-item {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818) 60%, transparent);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818) 5%, transparent);
  }

  .arch-layer-link {
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .arch-layer-link:hover {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 15%, transparent);
    color: var(--color-primary, #5CA3CA);
  }

  /* Flow indicator */
  .arch-flow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-light, #f6f6f6) 30%, transparent);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-flow {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818) 30%, transparent);
  }

  .arch-flow-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Detail cards */
  .arch-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .arch-details {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .arch-detail {
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-light, #f6f6f6) 6%, transparent);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-dark, #151515) 80%, transparent);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-detail {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-dark, #f7f7f7) 80%, transparent);
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818) 6%, transparent);
  }

  .arch-detail-summary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .arch-detail-summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .arch-detail-summary::marker {
    display: none;
    content: "";
  }

  .arch-detail-tag {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--layer-color) 20%, transparent);
    color: var(--layer-color);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .arch-detail-title {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-light, #f6f6f6);
    flex: 1;
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-detail-title {
    color: var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818);
  }

  .arch-detail-chevron {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-light, #f6f6f6) 40%, transparent);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-detail-chevron {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818) 40%, transparent);
  }

  .arch-detail[open] .arch-detail-chevron {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .arch-detail-body {
    padding: 0 1.25rem 1.25rem;
  }

  .arch-detail-body p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-light, #f6f6f6) 55%, transparent);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-detail-body p {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818) 55%, transparent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .arch-layer {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .arch-layer-label {
      min-width: unset;
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-light, #f6f6f6) 6%, transparent);
      padding: 0.625rem 0.875rem;
    }

    :root[data-theme="light"] .arch-layer-label {
      border-bottom-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-lightmode-light, #181818) 6%, transparent);
    }

    .arch-layer-items {
      padding: 0.625rem 0.875rem;
    }
  }
</style>
